## Document Structure

Quarto documents start with **YAML frontmatter** (the section between `---`):

```yaml
---
title: "My Document"
author: "Your Name"
date: today
format: html
---
```

Then you write in **Markdown** with optional **code blocks**:

````{markdown eval="false"}
# My Analysis

Some text here.

